          </h2>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row justify-center">
        <div class="lg:col-8">
  <div
    class="glass rounded-lg p-8 text-center mb-8 intersect:animate-fadeUp opacity-0"
  >
    <blockquote class="text-lg mb-4">
      "These stories gave my students permission to struggle with learning—and
